{
  "stem": "12029.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You had like a rickshaw, and a man used to sit in the back, and you sit in the front.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was like a little trolley, it was like a bicycle-- push.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] They decided that everybody has to go to the other part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And is it was so scared of food, we had to [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] get, somehow, food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had to leave our flat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A Pole came, and he said he would like to take all our furniture.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And for all the furniture, he gave us two kilos of bread and a half a kilo of butter, because we had to leave the flat.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But we had a lot of china, crockery, and crystal, and it was all packed in a crate.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my father said, this Pole won't take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I don't want the Germans to have it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we lived on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He threw it all down the stairs, that the German shouldn't get it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It broke.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to go back-- go to the other part of Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the time, already, my father's two sisters and a child went to [NON-ENGLISH] because we had some family there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And another sister of my father-- he had three sisters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And another sister of my father's, with a husband and child, went to another town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then in the ghetto was only left my parents, myself-- my brother worked in a different factory-- and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my youngest aunt's husband and child.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And when we work there-- and grandmother, we gave to a hospital.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] One day, before grandma went to the hospital, I went to see her to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
